    <item>
      <title>除非出现波动，否则国债基础交易仍将盛行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/treasury-basis-trade-stays-in-vogue-unless-volatility-erupts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基差交易是一种对冲基金利用国债和期货合约之间的微小价格差异获利的策略，如今这种策略又回来了。除非流动性紧缩扰乱这些市场，否则这种策略的受欢迎程度可能会提高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/treasury-basis-trade-stays-in-vogue-unless-volatility-erupts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:54:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗的齐托表示，银行风险交易是“当季投资”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/apollo-s-zito-says-bank-risk-deals-are-the-investment-du-jour</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 信贷部门副首席投资官约翰·齐托 (John Zito) 表示，承保银行资产负债表风险是“当下最热门的投资” — — 也是该公司一直精挑细选的投资项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/apollo-s-zito-says-bank-risk-deals-are-the-investment-du-jour</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:53:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
